But it's also important.
And this is especially important when it comes to a guy like Hogan.
He is a surprisingly popular Republican governor in a democratically-advantaged state.
He is ranked second in the approval rating among the country’s 50 governors.
Hogan is not a stubborn reactionary.
He showed a firm hand in the administration of the state and a commitment to its principles.
