“I also don’t like the idea that when a lot of people leave comments on the same topic, some immediately say it’s a so-called conundrum, instead of admitting that they’re dealing with a large group of disgruntled citizens.”
What the subordinates of the governor call a "concentrated spam attack", others would probably call an "active life position".
